    rating: "Pretty Bad"
    comments: "This just feels like a concept film overall as the overarching idea is pretty cool (it is just hard to believe with how low-budget this movie is); the plot structure is not laid out well as the movie just feels like two separate halves; the character writing is decent as the protagonist and antagonist are pretty interesting, but the rest of the characters feel pretty forced"
