  pacing: "Pacing is very fast as it tries to go through a lot of content in such a short period of time"
  climax: "Climax is executed very well as it helps highlight the visual effects and action"
  tone: "Tone is very post-apocalyptic and action-heavy (it's just they don't really capture the first part well because of the budget limitations)"
  final_notes: "The movie just feels like a concept film as it tries to do the most it can with such a low budget"
  overall: "Overall, this movie feels like a low-budget, concept film because it has an interesting idea and very well-executed action sequences, but the movie is constrained in how they can paint this world because of monetary restrictions"
